{
  "stem": "16442.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously, they must have put something into the coffee-- which later we found out it was true-- which calmed us and made us sort of a-- most people-- made those, like, couldn't care, you know?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Numb.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Certain numbness.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some of us who was crying 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some of us who got hysterical, so they were beaten and put back to lay there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this went on, I think, for about four weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the only thing we were able to keep, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the only thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were actually naked with our shoes on and no hair.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lucky there were no mirrors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only we saw each other, and we could imagine what we looked like.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I had a few girls, sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all left together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that point, yes, which [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lasted till about four to five weeks, like I said.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were called out in the middle of the day for a saal appel, a lineup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But our [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Czech girl told us, and everybody told us, if they come to choose somebody for work, we should try to go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As we were standing there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two SS came, looked us over, and about less than a half of the people who were standing in line-- motioned with his hand, cut off one part and put on one side.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then there was the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he cut off exactly by my row.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had the feeling that the smaller portion, whom he cut off, must have been chosen for work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one of my friends were there also.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
